nfiguration\n\n| Test | Behavior |\n|------|----------|\n| `stores dev-server-config in ctx.data` | Creates ctx.data['dev-server-config'] object |\n| `config includes port setting` | config.port is number |\n| `config includes asset routes from asset-pipeline` | Reads asset-manifest, creates routes with handler='asset' |\n| `config includes search index path` | config.searchIndexPath = '/search-index.json' if exists in output |\n| `config includes content routes` | Creates routes with handler='static' for each .html file |\n| `default port is 3000` | port defaults to 3000 |\n| `handles missing asset-pipeline data gracefully` | assetPaths = [] if no asset-manifest |\n\n**Config Structure:**\n```typescript\ninterface DevServerConfig {\n  port: number;\n  routes: Array<{ path: string; handler: string }>;\n  assetPaths: string[];\n  searchIndexPath: string;\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n#### C. sitemap.test.ts (8 tests)\n\nTests for `createSitemapPlugin()` - generates sitemap.xml\n\n| Test | Behavior |\n|------|----------|\n| `generates sitemap.xml in ctx.output` | Creates 'sitemap.xml' output |\n| `includes all content page URLs` | All .html files become URL entries |\n| `includes taxonomy tag page URLs` | Reads taxonomy-tags from ctx.data |\n| `includes feed.xml URL` | Includes if feed.xml exists in output |\n| `URLs use baseUrl from config` | Prepends baseUrl to all paths |\n| `sitemap is valid XML structure` | Contains proper XML declaration and tags |\n| `handles site with no tag pages` | Works without taxonomy plugin |\n\n**Output:**\n- `ctx.output['sitemap.xml']` = Valid XML with urlset containing loc entries\n\n---\n\n#### D. search-index.test.ts (7 tests)\n\nTests for `createSearchIndexPlugin()` - generates JSON search index\n\n| Test | Behavior |\n|------|----------|\n| `generates search-index.json in ctx.output` | Creates 'search-index.json' |\n| `index entries have title, slug, and plain text content` | Each entry has {slug, title, content} |\n| `HTML tags stripped from