h |\n| `handles empty content` | Returns defined (non-null) string |\n\n**Dependencies:** Uses `marked` library for markdown parsing\n\n**Syntax Support:**\n- Footnotes: `[^1]: Definition`\n- Containers: `:::type ... :::`\n- Basic markdown: headers, emphasis, etc.\n\n---\n\n### 7. PACKAGE.JSON - DEPENDENCIES & SCRIPTS\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"bench-ssg-toolkit\",\n  \"version\": \"1.0.0\",\n  \"description\": \"SSG Toolkit benchmark - static site generator with DAG plugin system\",\n  \"main\": \"dist/core/index.js\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"build\": \"tsc\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint src/ tests/\",\n    \"test\": \"vitest run\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"express\": \"^5.2.1\",\n    \"marked\": \"^17.0.2\",\n    \"@types/express\": \"^5.0.6\",\n    \"@types/marked\": \"^5.0.2\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"typescript\": \"^5.9.3\",\n    \"vitest\": \"^2.1.9\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^8.57.1\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/parser\": \"^7.18.0\",\n    \"@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin\": \"^7.18.0\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Key Dependencies:**\n- `marked` (17.0.2): Markdown to HTML parser\n- `express` (5.2.1): Web framework (for dev-server plugin)\n- `typescript` (5.9.3): TypeScript compiler\n- `vitest` (2.1.9): Test runner\n\n---\n\n### 8. TSCONFIG.JSON - COMPILATION SETTINGS\n\n```json\n{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"strict\": true,                  // Enable all strict type checks\n    \"target\": \"ES2022\",              // Output target\n    \"module\": \"Node16\",              // Module format (Node 16+ ES modules)\n    \"moduleResolution\": \"Node16\",    // Use Node.js resolution\n    \"outDir\": \"./dist\",              // Compiled output directory\n    \"rootDir\": \"./src\",              // Source root\n    \"declaration\": true,             // Generate .d.ts files\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,         // CJS/ESM interop\n    \"skipLibCheck\": true             // Skip type checking of .d.ts files\n  },\n  \"include\":